The paper discusses the classification of hyperspectral images using statistical learning methods, which involves techniques from computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
